name: Texas State Optical Galveston
tag_list: optometrist, galveston, eye-doctor, downtown-galveston, texas, eye-exam, galveston-island, eye-care, eyeglasses, contacts
overview:
TSO Galveston provides eye care services to residents of Galveston, Texas. Their optometrists offer prescriptions for contact lenses and eyeglasses as well as a variety of eye exams and eye care services.

Eye Exams offered:

  • Comprehensive eye exams
  • Pediatric eye exams
  • Advanced eye examinations for people with eye conditions

The optometry practice utilizes the latest advancements in eye exam equipment which allows their eye doctors to diagnose with greater accuracy eye diseases and the causes of bad or low vision.

This practice also provides a collection of eyewear from different brand name designer frames manufacturers. They also carry a big selection of sunglasses.

Their optometrists also provide contact lens fitting and a variety of contact lenses are available in the store.

This eye care clinic serves the Downtown Galveston Island area.
